Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a new cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put it in the washing machine this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it somewhere I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tsukasa, help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vinega{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it in for you, so give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came over to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah welcome, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gal-game that came out recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll just borrow some of your manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's an adult game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but either she didn't notice, or she's going to pretend to not see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's Traffic Safety week we're cracking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like doing thorough checks...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or explaining all of the traffic rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes people snap at me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at your daily life, Nee-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.12,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,So scary, so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not convincing at all when you talk about rules and safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that this year's cold is especially persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better get it taken care of soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from my number, it's probably going to take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll read a book while I'm waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ando-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ando Shigeo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara Miyuki-san, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishiyama Mariko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to pay more attention to my surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are almost at the final terminal, Kamata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-huh, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was teaching Tsukasa how to send text messages the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been playing with her cell phone so much, yet she still doesn't know how to text. {splitting the audio here would suck, maybe edit this? - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because she's so excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she sends a text whenever anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard to be on the receiving end of that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think you need to worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the type that's all gung-ho in the beginning, {split - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but loses interest as time goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, there are people who never grow out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I got another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that they get tired of it, but rather they just can't last that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Want me to buy some soy milk on the way home?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the stuff after it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling she's having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I can barely recognize half of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's finally getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but how about we stop sending tons of texts to family members?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure how to send a text message on my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so easy, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're so helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the master now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say much for that stench.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, it smelled so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a lot of entries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you don't want me to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not picking up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll call her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you pick up your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it stopped ringing, so I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what's the point if you don't notice it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know where it is to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There really is no point in you having a cell phone, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So about this weekend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One sec, my dad's calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spend too much time on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad got mad at me because I'm talking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought your house would be so strict on that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were in the middle of a fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me that in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime, anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,point cards possess mysterious powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you finally realize it, {split, although I have no idea where I split it since kotana speaks way too fast - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've bought stuff you weren't planning to buy in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't plan anything at all, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kind of understand, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this town, there is an Animate and a Gamers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though she knows there are two anime shops in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a person that will go to both and buy the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Girl, A! {I capitalized it here since the Legendary Girl A is a name.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the Legendary Girl A shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got the new Haruhi DVD Vol. 5 in stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Limited edition...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal edition...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ready, desu! {Desu?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And plenty more related miscellaneous goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, as long as she notices as many new products as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will buy them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get the Aquarium Age special bookmark today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better go to Gamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to spend the night on Saturday and Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that way we could play all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we play, we always play at our house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my dad's at home a lot because of his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, so I can't be responsible for what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Konata's house is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard all about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your house is a shrine and you two are shrine maidens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.47,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys normally wear yellow hakama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is that the first thing he has to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kona-chan's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an amazing room, just as I'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, cute~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This door...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the "forbidden door" where all of your secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that cannot be exposed, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One that must never be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I share that with my dad, so they're all in his archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you share it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, your dad's an author, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you get stuck on the novels or gal-games that your dad makes? {Stuck? As in, being stuck in a game and not knowing what to do next? Reconfirm.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't write that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes that kind of world, yet he's never thought about writing one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call it a bystanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he plays gal-games and simulation games whenever he's free,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he doesn't feel the need to make them in his work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been surprising me so much that I don't even know how react!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the Izumi house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, my dad followed me around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried saying, "Dad, take a hike!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a little too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he got mad at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You could at least say, 'I hate you daddy!'"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not too sure about that correction either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my dad's mindset and what you're thinking are slightly out of sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we see a lot more l33t-speak on TV, nowadays. {L33t? Really? :O}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're pretty deep into this stuff, yet you don't talk like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I chat it looks like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this even Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can read it, I'll consider it my defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can you season the salad then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you always do household chores, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might get a little better, too, Kagami, if you actually did chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the image I've seen in my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One guy and three high school girls having dinner together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.13,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Heaven on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.35,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a pretty common situation in gal-games,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:41.65,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister is Tohsaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though completely unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure gets cold at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've worn a jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, a shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say my wish three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they come so suddenly, it's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to succeed one day and have my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you sure like to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But realistically, that's totally impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only think the legend became true because no one has succeeded yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever dream at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to drink some too, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You switched hair styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you let us use the bath first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the same parts, {split, but it sucks. - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but depending on who uses them, the image changes so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an album.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed much since you were little, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you seem really close with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So young!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we look alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She better not be jail-bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at my dad and always wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What exactly did my mom like about him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you look so similar to your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what kind of guys do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... when you put it that way, I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Mom could have been with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said something about how they were childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't think that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after searching around, she ended up with Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty brutal, even to your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After looking at Mom, I wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of characters in manga or games who seem mature for their age...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or adults who seem very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want us to respond to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been nice if Yuki-chan could have come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she said she was busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send Yuki-chan a mail so she's not too lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki may pay too much attention to it, so I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm glad to hear you guys are having fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now, I'm working hard to take care of my homework."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please invite me next time{\fscx300}-{\r}"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot I had homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.18,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,My class didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shooting star earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make your wish shorter, it might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Research on how to make your wish shorter for shooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop procrastinating and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't understand this part of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata is Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki is Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what kind of nickname would you give Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the other reading of "kagami" and call her Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that totally makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really brings out her boldness and strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can turn it into this "kyou", too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not what I had in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'd better not mention this to Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had to give yourself a nickname, what would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuka-chan or Kasa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's hard to use my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have an image of Tsukasa going "hihi" all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my intention either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'm going to call you Hi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, why not? {Are, are = What, why not?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't it feel a little awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you decide your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want revenge, Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could she be calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's confusing, so stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just call me Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with having a nickname like Kona-chan or Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Kagami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, she actually did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait, Kagami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Kagami-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please just use my name normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oha-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not, Lucky Channel is now entering the 10th episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the navigator, Kogami Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the assistant, Shiraishi Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This week is character introduction #4!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi Kagami edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the series, she is the well-known "brunt end of jokes" character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't she simply the tsundere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The setting is so easy to see and is so uncreative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your information...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it is rather crude to label Kagami-san as a tsundere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do we truly understand the respective qualities of a tsundere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the word tsundere...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been so degraded that its definition has been muddled. {split - Flyer} {Sounds awkward. Maybe "...has lost its original meaning."}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the word tsundere was first introduced in 2002...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the internet term,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but its original definition was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone who is tsuntsun at first, then later becomes deredere."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it signifies the change in personalities over time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nowadays, {split - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's become the nom de jour to describe a character's bipolar tendencies. {Nom de what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, someone who is outwardly tsuntsun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet deep down deredere,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is how it is generally understood to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I hereby declare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That this is an obvious mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must now restore the original meaning of the word tsundere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By bringing everyone's attention to the true meaning, {split - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can prevent the deterioration of modern language!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kagami isn't a tsundere, then what is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure about this complicated stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if she isn't a tsundere,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is there some other word that we can use to describe her? {not enough time, edit maybe? - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there is but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool-dere or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dere-tsun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with tsundere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have our viewers help us think of a new expression to replace "tsundere"! {changed from "some new expression" - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delegating it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, everyone watching TV right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yes, you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us think of a good word to describe characters like Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rewrite the book of "common knowledge".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Complete Tsundere Register.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to us on the radio or visit our homepage for more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting for your passionate responses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots, and lots, and lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bii.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bii!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send us stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I sure talked a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that was my best one yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, well, I've never spoken this much,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think I did a pretty good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm having dinner with your studio's manager and producer in a bit... {changed from "I'm going to have" - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...? {messy, might want to add something - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To discuss some matters that might concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if the person just can't take the hints...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, aren't you still working part-time at CoCo*chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just during the day, so I don't exactly make too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the barbecue restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I still work at the yakiniku-ya, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's getting a little too private, so please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, how's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you sing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
