Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:37.72,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,This song was really popular when we \Nwere in kindergarten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:38.98,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.02,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.27,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.55,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,My sisters used to sing it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:49.42,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,Songs from an earlier generation \Nthat your older relatives know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.94,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,tend to be absorbed more naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:24.06,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your voice cracked...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:25.56,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:26.91,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next week on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.49,0:22:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with ordering soup when you're going out to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pretty depressing when the soup splashes and a little gets on your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry roux is the worst with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:22:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then if you're wearing one of your favorite shirts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.51,0:23:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it could ruin your whole day. {split - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when you buy a boxed lunch that contains sauce at a convenience store,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you try to keep it as level as you so you don't spill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.80,0:23:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you get home and look inside the bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you see the soup all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.55,0:23:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you lose your appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, it's nice when they put warm and cold foods in separate bags for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when they put cold drinks in a bag with your magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the magazine absorbs all of the condensed water and gets soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making you wonder, "What was the point!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next week: "The various ways to spend Christmas Eve"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
